data: One of the dozen Argon outposts destroyed during the First Xenon Conflict, Morning Star was only rediscovered after the most recent Jump Gate realignment, with archaeologists still uncovering many of the homes and factories laid to waste by the Terraformers during that conflict.\n\nThough the Argon Federation has begun the process of resettling the system, work has been slow, as there have always been higher priorities for investment among the more strongly contested border sectors. Naturally, this did not prevent independent Argon entrepreneurs from establishing their own businesses in the vacant space of Morning Star, and today the system is bustling with civilian traffic.
